# TacDent Frontend — overview

Marketing + appointment-booking site for a dental clinic. It is a thin client over a
.NET API; it has no database or business logic of its own.

## Stack (do not assume older versions)
- Next.js 16 (App Router) · React 19 · TypeScript (strict) · Tailwind CSS v4.
- **shadcn/ui** for components (built on **Base UI**, not Radix) · **lucide-react** icons.
- **react-hook-form + zod** (`@hookform/resolvers`) for forms · **sonner** for toasts.
- **embla-carousel** (`embla-carousel-react` + `-autoplay`) for sliders · **next-themes** for dark mode.
- `cva` + `clsx` + `tailwind-merge` (`cn` helper) for class composition.
- Path alias: `@/*` -> `./src/*`. (Note: Swiper is gone — use the shadcn `Carousel`.)

## ⚠️ Next.js 16 is newer than your training data
APIs, conventions, and file structure may differ from what you remember. Before writing
Next-specific code (routing, `params`/`searchParams`, caching, `next/image`, metadata,
server actions), verify against `node_modules/next/dist/docs/` or current docs. Do not
"fix" code to an older pattern you recognize.

